text:
Thank you for the great shoot.
It was really amazing, captivating even.
Hehe... Thank you for the wonderful compliment.

No, really, it's like you're carrying off
the dress with such elegance.

Maybe it's your poise,
you move in a way that really showcases the dress.

...If that's the case,
then the dress must have accentuated me.

What do you think? You seemed to
bring out the charm of the dress, Natsuha.

Yeah,
I'll have to make it even more stunning on stage.
After all, this dress is my partner!
